description: Ingredient Sub is a handy and simple tool to help with many common ingredient substitutions while cooking. Ran out of brown sugar? Ask Ingredient Sub what you can use instead and it will respond if there is a substitute, with specific quantities and various options. Includes over 100 common ingredient substitutions.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Ingredient Sub what can I substitute for chicken broth.
Alexa, ask Ingredient Sub what can I use instead of brown sugar.
name: Ingredient Sub
shortDescription: Out of an ingredient? Ask Ingredient Sub what can be substituted in place of missing ingredients while cooking.
